select count(*) as aggregate from `admins` where `role` != 'super-admin'
select * from `users` order by `created_at` desc limit 7
select sum(`charge`) as aggregate from `transactions` where `charge` > 0

select count(CASE WHEN status = "completed"  THEN status END) AS completed, count(CASE WHEN status = "processing" THEN status END) AS processing, count(CASE WHEN status = "pending"    THEN status END) AS pending, count(CASE WHEN status = "progress"   THEN status END) AS progress, count(CASE WHEN status = "partial"    THEN status END) AS partial, count(CASE WHEN status = "canceled"   THEN status END) AS canceled, count(CASE WHEN status = "refunded"   THEN status END) AS refunded from `orders`

select count(id) as totalDepositCount, count(CASE WHEN status = "completed"  THEN status END) AS completed, count(CASE WHEN status = "pending"    THEN status END) AS pending, count(CASE WHEN status = "rejected"   THEN status END) AS rejected from `deposits`
